				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="blockquote" style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong><a href="https://youtu.be/iYYRH4apXDo" target="_blank">For here am I sitting in my tin can</a></strong><br /> <strong><a href="https://youtu.be/iYYRH4apXDo" target="_blank">Far above the world</a></strong><br /> <strong><a href="https://youtu.be/iYYRH4apXDo" target="_blank">Planet Earth is blue</a></strong><br /> <strong><a href="https://youtu.be/iYYRH4apXDo" target="_blank">And there's nothing I can do</a></strong></p> </div> <blockquote> <p><strong>Illac</strong><br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598636825" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <ul> <li>This Tale is for <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/thaumiel">Project Thaumiel</a></strong>.</li> <li>This Tale's title is an interpretation + rough Latin translation of the etymology behind the name “Harkness”, <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/sr-researcher-james-a-harkness-personnel-file">Billith's Author Avatar</a></strong>.</li> <li>“Hate-filled Light” is the “Hateful Star”, which is the primary aggressor against humanity in Billith's Proposal. It is also a reference to the old <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1548">SCP-1548</a></strong> before it was deleted, which <strong><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180625002922/http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-1548">you can find in the Internet Archive</a></strong>. Within this Tale are references to a few other Mainlist pages, too.</li> </ul> <p>Hope you enjoy! :)</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;&nbsp;▷&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p>▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justiceprevails" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6477711&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598636825" alt="JusticePrevails" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6477711)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justiceprevails" >JusticePrevails</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stephlynch" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1802367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598636825" alt="stephlynch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1802367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stephlynch" >stephlynch</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598636825" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3352053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1598636825" alt="Cerastes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3352053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" >Cerastes</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" ><img class="small"